iceFlake
Open Compute Platform

Vibhaj Rajan <vibhaj8@gmail.com>

Subsystems
	DB: 	Database
	IO: 	Input/Output
	NS: 	Name Service
	RT: 	Runtime
	FN:		Callback
	SI:		Smart Interface
	UI:		User Interface

Definitions
	Service: 	Functions with single argument - a Map: an array of key-value pairs, 
				returning a Map with all results
				Return Map must contain Status Keys ( 'valid', 'msg', 'details' )
	Message:	Standard Service Invocation Definition ( SSID )
	Workflow:	Array of Messages
	Navigator:	Serialized SSID String without having array as values
	State:		Central State Registry
	Config:		Central Configuration Registry

Inspirations:
	DB:		Codefest 2010 Website ( JR Harshath )
	IO:		Yahoo! Buzz
	NS:		TPR Executive
	RT:		GSoC 2011 DSpace RESTClient
	FN:		Yahoo! Buzz
	SI:		FireSpark
	UI:		Orbitnote

